%% Graph 1: Prompt-Era vs. Context-Era -- What shifts when you move from prompting to context engineering

flowchart LR
    subgraph PE["🅿️ Prompt Engineering Era"]
        direction TB
        PE1["✏️ Craft the perfect prompt"]
        PE2["💬 Single interaction"]
        PE3["🔄 Retry with better wording"]
        PE4["❓ Why did the model ignore me?"]
        PE1 --> PE2 --> PE3 --> PE4
    end

    subgraph CE["🏗️ Context Engineering Era"]
        direction TB
        CE1["📐 Design the information environment"]
        CE2["⚙️ Multi-step agent workflows"]
        CE3["🗂️ Curate, compress, isolate context"]
        CE4["🔍 What conflicting context diluted it?"]
        CE1 --> CE2 --> CE3 --> CE4
    end

    PE -- "The Shift" --> CE

    style PE fill:#f9f0f0,stroke:#c0392b,color:#333
    style CE fill:#edf7ed,stroke:#27ae60,color:#333
